TITLE: Configuring Storybook Stories for React List Component with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code configures Storybook stories for a React List component using standard TypeScript. It explicitly types the meta object and defines two stories: Empty and OneItem, with proper typing for the Story object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/blob/next/docs/_snippets/list-story-with-subcomponents.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

