TITLE: Exporting Accessibility Parameters in Storybook Preview - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet sets up accessibility parameters in Storybook‚Äôs configuration file by exporting a Preview object. It specifies rule settings for 'autocomplete' and 'image-alt', and allows manual control of automatic checks via the 'manual' flag. It requires integration with a specific JavaScript framework and set up for Storybook.
