TITLE: Configuring Storybook with JSON Story Indexer in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up a custom indexer for JSON story files in Storybook using JavaScript. It defines the indexer function, specifies file patterns for stories, and adds the custom indexer to the existing indexers.
