TITLE: Svelte Component Story with CSF Format
DESCRIPTION: Svelte-specific implementation using Component Story Format (CSF) showing delayed typing interactions with play function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/blob/next/docs/_snippets/my-component-play-function-with-delay.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
<script module>
  import { defineMeta } from '@storybook/addon-svelte-csf';

  import { userEvent, within } from 'storybook/test';

  import MyComponent from './MyComponent.svelte';

  const { Story } = defineMeta({
    component: MyComponent,
  });
</script>

<Story
  name="DelayedStory"
  play={async ({ canvasElement }) => {
    const canvas = within(canvasElement);

    const exampleElement = canvas.getByLabelText('example-element');

    await userEvent.type(exampleElement, 'random string', {
