DESCRIPTION: Defines Storybook story metadata for a Svelte component using TypeScript 4.9 'satisfies' operator for precise type checking, while removing the 'foo' property from controls. Requires @storybook/svelte, YourComponent import, and TS 4.9+. Exports a 'meta' object that conforms to Meta<typeof YourComponent>, disabling the specified UI control.
