TITLE: Converting Story Indexers to Experimental Indexers in Storybook
DESCRIPTION: Code diff showing how to migrate from the deprecated storyIndexers to the new experimental_indexers API. The key change is using createIndex instead of indexer and returning indexInputs from parsed CSF files.
SOURCE: https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/blob/next/MIGRATION.md#2025-04-22_snippet_61

