TITLE: Implementing List Stories in Solid with TypeScript 4.9 Syntax
DESCRIPTION: Creates a Storybook story for a Solid.js List component using TypeScript 4.9 with 'satisfies' operator. It imports the Unchecked story from ListItem stories and composes them in the render function.
