TITLE: Global Source Code Transformation in Storybook Preview
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to globally transform source code in Storybook Docs using a regular expression to remove the arrow at the beginning of a function that returns a string.
SOURCE: https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook/blob/next/code/addons/docs/docs/recipes.md#2025-04-22_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const SOURCE_REGEX = /^\(\) => `(.*)`$/;
export const parameters = {
  docs: {
    source: {
      transform: (src, storyContext) => {
        const match = SOURCE_REGEX.exec(src);
        return match ? match[1] : src;
      },
    },
  },
};
```

